# Cubrim License

The Cubrim Rust crate license is defined in `code/cubrim-rs/LICENSE`.

Summary:

- Non-commercial use is available under the PolyForm Noncommercial License
  1.0.0, with Cubrim-specific notices in `code/cubrim-rs/LICENSE`.
- Commercial use requires a separate paid commercial license. The draft terms
  are in `code/cubrim-rs/LICENSE-COMMERCIAL.md`.
- Temporary canonical publication target: `https://cubrim.com/legal/cubrim-license`.
- Future canonical publication target: `https://legal.arcanada.ai/policies/cubrim/license/v1.0`.

This repository-level file is a pointer for repository hosts. The Cargo package
uses `code/cubrim-rs/LICENSE` as its `license-file`.
